messageBody:
I was surprised and glad to see we now have 310 members registered
today. This is the highest total I have seen. When you are writing
in QS and someone sees you, let them know about its advantages and
history. Then direct them to our group for more information. Many
people stumble across the site, I am sure, but a little judicious
proselytizing certainly couldn't hurt.

The two question poll I created has been answered by fewer than 30
people. If you want to get your vote in, please do so within the next
two weeks. I will be on vacation, but I plan to close the poll in
Early May. Thanks for participating.

Paige

I was surprised and glad to see we now have 310 members registered
today.  This is the highest total I have seen.  When you are writing
in QS and someone sees you, let them know about its advantages and
history.  Then direct them to our group for more information.  Many
people stumble across the site, I am sure, but a little judicious
proselytizing certainly couldn't hurt.

The two question poll I created has been answered by fewer than 30
people.  If you want to get your vote in, please do so within the next
two weeks.  I will be on vacation, but I plan to close the poll in
Early May.  Thanks for participating.

Paige
